    "passive": {
      "name": "Shadow of Styx",
      "description": "Helcurt remains in Prowler state until spotted by the enemy team, gaining 15% extra Movement Speed, and continuously regenerating (30% Total Physical Attack) HP if he has not dealt any damage.\nHe gains 50% extra Attack Speed and 50% extra Movement Speed (decreasing over time) for 4s upon being spotted and leaves Prowler state 0.75s later.\nAny hero killed after being hit by Helcurt leaves a dark fog that explodes and spreads with a cooldown of 10s. Helcurt Conceals himself while within the dark fog.\n|quote=He who hides in the shadow.",
